{"tid":930091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平同志為鞏固我國與非洲傳統友誼，辛苦了！","createTime":"2018-12-06T05:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T05:25:16.000Z","uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"34b960b3884ffb88b546f67693d5075e19658bcf","tid":930091,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"何志平同志不怕身犯險境，走在一帶一路、十三五規劃最前線。為左突破以美國為首之帝國主義對我國封鎖，鞏固我國與非洲諸國自古以用鮮血築成的傳統友誼，不惜冒險深入敵陣，企圖由內在瓦解邪惡帝國主義。<br />\n<br />\n可惜非常不幸，美倭魔高一丈，設局陷害何志平同志。現我黨委任何同志為中共中央美國紐約監獄黨委總書記，望何同志繼續在國外發揮餘熱，緊隨習核心思想，完成中國夢。"},{"pid":"ffec7c5cdc2559b57bb71516b7018dbdf4939eea","tid":930091,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNBgyNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNBgyNN.png&h=c86f5d78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRf1KUs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRf1KUs.png&h=02ec638a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4217bf4757e9c6f54ba51de701a0081f110e35f6","tid":930091,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:25:16.000Z","msg":"收到消息,會放過肥平"}]}